Key Match Events: Jayson Tatum hit a game-winning 30-foot shot at the buzzer to lift the Celtics past the Raptors in overtime
Pre-Game Insights: It's still very early in the season, but Jayson Tatum fixing his jumpshot could end up being one of the biggest stories of the year
Post-Match Reflections: Jayson Tatum spoke about his buzzer-beating overtime 3-pointer, saying 'I got a lot of problems in life. Confidence has never been one of them.'
Al Horford thanks Tatum for helping the Celtics avoid a second overtime period
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Raptors were winless on the road, 2-12, and lost 7 straight, while the Celtics were 11-3
Jayson Tatum is ranked 3rd in top off the bounce 3 pt attempts and percentage this season
Jayson Tatum is ranked 5th in most 35-point games this season
